The changes have been committed and pushed. Here's a summary of what was    
  done:                                                                       
                                                                              
  ## Summary                                                                  
                                                                              
  The issue requested adding a new term **"immunocytochemistry"** to EFO.     
                                                                              
  **Key finding**: The term already exists in OBI (Ontology for Biomedical    
  Investigations) as **OBI:0002174**, so following EFO policy, it was imported
  rather than creating a duplicate EFO-native term.                           
                                                                              
  ### Changes made:                                                           
                                                                              
  1. src/ontology/iri_dependencies/obi_terms.txt — Added http://purl.         
  obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002174 to import this term from OBI                 
  2. src/ontology/imports/obi_import.owl — Regenerated to include OBI:0002174 
  with:                                                                       
      • Label: immunocytochemistry                                            
      • Definition: *"An immuno staining assay in which samples of intact     
      cells are examined that have had most, if not all, of their surrounding 
      extracellular matrix removed"*                                          
      • Parent: OBI:0000070 (assay) → EFO:0002694 (experimental process)      
  3. .gitignore — Added src/ontology/imports/obi_bot.owl (build artifact)     
                                                                              
  ### Hierarchy:                                                              
                                                                              
  immunocytochemistry (OBI:0002174) → assay (OBI:0000070) → experimental      
  process (EFO:0002694)                                                       
                                                                              
  This correctly places immunocytochemistry under the requested parent        
  (EFO:0002694 experimental process) via the OBI assay hierarchy.

